Overview

Demonstrates successful execution of a qualified lead through the complete HyperSync Lead Operating System.

Shows operational movement through:

Lead Intake OS
→ Lead Process OS
→ Lead Outbound OS
→ Lead System OS

with successful governance updates and final completion.

Recording Objectives

Demonstrate:

Lead creation

Intake processing

Process validation

CRM preparation

Campaign activation

Audit logging

Final completion
Recording Flow
Section 1

Lead Intake

Show:

Lead enters trigger sheet

Lead enters staging

Pipeline log update

Event logger update
Section 2

Lead Process

Show:

Lead enters PRC trigger

Sanitizer execution

Validation pass

CRM prep completion
Section 3

Lead Outbound

Show:

CRM sync

Campaign enrollment

Nurture activation
Section 4

Lead System

Show:

Audit log entry

State snapshot update

System completion
Success Criteria

Visible evidence of:

Lead_ID continuity

Correlation_ID continuity

Successful status progression

Governance updates

Final completed state
